properties.Name: ShipmentEvent
properties.Description: An event that is associated with a Shipment to track its progress or status as it is shipped, stored, in customs etc.

Columns.Name: ShipmentId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Shipment.

Columns.Name: ShipmentEventTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Shipment Event Type.

Columns.Name: ShipmentEventStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The start timestamp of the associated Shipment Event.

Columns.Name: ShipmentEventEndTimestamp
Columns.Description: The end timestamp of the associated Shipment Event.

Columns.Name: ShipmentEventStatusId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Shipment Event Status.

Columns.Name: ShipmentEventNote
Columns.Description: Notes, comments or additional information regarding the Shipment Event.

Columns.Name: ShippingLocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Shipping Location.
